data.description: MLS# 270594 Well maintained and spacious home on a large lot featuring 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, 2 living rooms, finished basement and cellar. The original hardwood flooring, family dining area, laundry room, large kitchen, and expansive basement make this home stand apart. Pride in ownership is showcased with recently painted exterior and interior, updated bathrooms and new roof. Step into the backyard and you are greeted to a beautiful fully fenced yard with green grass, garden areas, shed and fully covered handicap accessible deck. This property is within walking distance to Jason Lee Elementary school, parks, and a membership only community pool. Sellers are including a one year home warranty with the sale of the home. Located in central Richland and minutes away from anything, this home is a must see.
